(24598, 'Paroxedep cr 37.5 mg 10 enteric f.c.tabs.', 'باروكسيديب سي ار 37.5مجم 10 اقراص', '27', '39', 'Paroxetine', 'Apex pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد للاكتئاب -- علاج الامراض النفسية -- يحسن الحالة المزاجية -- يؤخذ تحت اشراف طبيب', 'Psychiatric.antidepressants', '37.5 mg', 'Paroxetine is indicated for the management of depression, obsessive-compulsive disorder, panic disorder, social anxiety disorder, generalized anxiety disorder, posttraumatic stress disorder.[L3358] One form of paroxetine, commercially known as Brisdelle, is used to manage mild to moderate vasomotor symptoms of menopause.[L7703] Off-label, paroxetine may be used for the treatment of premature ejaculation or irritable bowel syndrome (IBS).[A1093,A181754,A181904]', '', '', 3612, '2025-03-01', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
